<br>
Some sort of snare...hey...I can convince the earth to take shape..and rise up in the form of a powerful elemental...but I can't make a vine rap around a mobs leg?<br>
<br>
Summon Flying Carpet...has no speed effects...just permanant levitation while in zone.  Uses?  Not too sure...but it certainly goes well with wedding cake and fireworks!<br>
<br>
Summon Mirror....I'm a mage...whatdyou expect?<br>
<br>
Summon Designated Driver...only works with Summon Flying Carpet...and Alcohol Tolerance of 150+.<br>
<br>
Summon Bow..seriously...we got the arrows and quiver.<br>
<br>
Summon Red Ruby Slippers..(gate..charges x2)..There's no place like home...theres on place like home...<br>
<br>
Some of these are for humor only...a few are serious.  Whats your take?<br>
